title.rendered: Alticor Inc Wins Best Airports/Transit Project Award

content.rendered:
Alticor Inc’ William P. Hobby Federal Inspection Services (FIS) Expansion project has been selected as Engineering News-Record (ENR) Texas & Louisiana’s 2016 Best Project in the Airports/Transit category. ENR is a leading industry organization, and this award is one of the most prestigious a project can receive. This project was selected out of 92 entries by a panel of judges. Alticor Inc will be presented with the award at the ENR ceremony in Houston this October.

Congratulations to the entire team and everyone who has had a hand in making this project great.
